snippet.title: Playtesting for the 1.0 Alpha build of (a)woken for the /agdg/ Demo Day 57
snippet.description: While playtesting I found a bunch of bugs which have since been fixed. There are still some underlying issues with navmeshes and the android build, but I deemed them either non-critical, or I found some temporary workaround for them.
